 in reducing aggression in a variety of neurologic and psychiatric conditions. Its exact mechanism of action is unknown, but may involve central &beta;-adrenergic blockade,15 peripheral effects on the sympathetic nervous system,11,16 or serotonergic blockade.1<br />\n<br />\n利申：食緊20mg/day"},{"pid":"4b008ce430f83498ab862cac5ed3a1a2e27262cb","tid":2348700,"uid":44107,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T13:59:37.000Z","msg":"Beta blocker 最彈之一<br />\n個心有事唔知食左會死人<br />\nConduction block/profound hypotension + bradycardia 可以bye bye"},{"pid":"b0517da31fc54a3dc38b99340d17b795c631a04c","tid":2348700,"uid":55192,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:12:49.000Z","msg":"你有幾多貨？想點賣"},{"pid":"4b11f5817279ddfc7e92c680aa58130bd4962dac","tid":2348700,"uid":308494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b008ce430f83498ab862cac5ed3a1a2e27262cb","tid":2348700,"uid":44107,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T13:59:37.000Z","msg":"Beta blocker 最彈之一<br />\n個心有事唔知食左會死人<br />\nConduction block/profound hypotension + bradycardia 可以bye bye"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T16:15:49.000Z","msg":"我因為太焦慮 有食過 想問下咩叫彈?反彈?定危險？之前個醫生話安全既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b55ed4e6b8a6ada7adff4629c6c0c0016a67b7","tid":2348700,"uid":286206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:13:13.000Z","msg":"醫生一開就開兩個月兩個月比我儲埋一堆 但其實感覺上無乜用 真係好焦慮果時就直接xanax <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但有時心跳好快隻藥又真係有d用"},{"pid":"2a96ebe08f57c5c1c2570e735e1b0b3befbf1778","tid":2348700,"uid":12447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57b55ed4e6b8a6ada7adff4629c6c0c0016a67b7","tid":2348700,"uid":286206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:13:13.000Z","msg":"醫生一開就開兩個月兩